<emphasis id="4095EAFE2439BD60FF37DC2A1F2FA183" box="[151,1040,616,642]" italics="true" pageId="39" pageNumber="40">A. Fernández, F. Stauffer, R. Riina, K. Walter-Weissbeck &amp; O. Kunert 10087</emphasis>
